name: Labyrinth 2 (itch)
description: Labyrinth 2 is not the kind of labyrinth game you expect, it is more difficult, with more fun and it has better graphics. Collect coins in every level and destroy extra objects in the labyrinth to reach the trophy if you find a way out of the labyrinth. Enjoy Labyrinth 2 on the go and find a way out of various small or huge labyrinths. Find hidden trophys and more in the mobile version of Labyrinth 2
